        <updateDate>2019-06-06T14:10:45Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><strong>Income-Based Repayment Debt Forgiveness Act</strong></p> <p>This bill modifies the requirements for calculating taxable income to exclude from the gross income of an individual any income that is attributable to the discharge of a federal student loan pursuant to a federal program or law that provides for income contingent or income-based repayment of the loan. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
